[
  {
    "id": 6059,
    "number": 1,
    "key": "92:1",
    "textAr": "وَٱلَّيْلِ إِذَا يَغْشَىٰ",
    "textEn": "By the night when it covers",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6060,
    "number": 2,
    "key": "92:2",
    "textAr": "وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "And [by] the day when it appears",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6061,
    "number": 3,
    "key": "92:3",
    "textAr": "وَمَا خَلَقَ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلْأُنثَىٰٓ",
    "textEn": "And [by] He who created the male and female,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6062,
    "number": 4,
    "key": "92:4",
    "textAr": "إِنَّ سَعْيَكُمْ لَشَتَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "Indeed, your efforts are diverse.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6063,
    "number": 5,
    "key": "92:5",
    "textAr": "فَأَمَّا مَنْ أَعْطَىٰ وَٱتَّقَىٰ",
    "textEn": "As for he who gives and fears Allāh",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6064,
    "number": 6,
    "key": "92:6",
    "textAr": "وَصَدَّقَ بِٱلْحُسْنَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And believes in the best [reward],",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6065,
    "number": 7,
    "key": "92:7",
    "textAr": "فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلْيُسْرَىٰ",
    "textEn": "We will ease him toward ease.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6066,
    "number": 8,
    "key": "92:8",
    "textAr": "وَأَمَّا مَنۢ بَخِلَ وَٱسْتَغْنَىٰ",
    "textEn": "But as for he who withholds and considers himself free of need",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6067,
    "number": 9,
    "key": "92:9",
    "textAr": "وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلْحُسْنَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And denies the best [reward],",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6068,
    "number": 10,
    "key": "92:10",
    "textAr": "فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلْعُسْرَىٰ",
    "textEn": "We will ease him toward difficulty.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6069,
    "number": 11,
    "key": "92:11",
    "textAr": "وَمَا يُغْنِى عَنْهُ مَالُهُۥٓ إِذَا تَرَدَّىٰٓ",
    "textEn": "And what will his wealth avail him when he falls?",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6070,
    "number": 12,
    "key": "92:12",
    "textAr": "إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا لَلْهُدَىٰ",
    "textEn": "Indeed, [incumbent] upon Us is guidance.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6071,
    "number": 13,
    "key": "92:13",
    "textAr": "وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلْـَٔاخِرَةَ وَٱلْأُولَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And indeed, to us belongs the Hereafter and the first [life].",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6072,
    "number": 14,
    "key": "92:14",
    "textAr": "فَأَنذَرْتُكُمْ نَارًا تَلَظَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "So I have warned you of a Fire which is blazing.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 595,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6073,
    "number": 15,
    "key": "92:15",
    "textAr": "لَا يَصْلَىٰهَآ إِلَّا ٱلْأَشْقَى",
    "textEn": "None will [enter to] burn therein except the most wretched one",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 596,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6074,
    "number": 16,
    "key": "92:16",
    "textAr": "ٱلَّذِى كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "Who had denied and turned away.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 596,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6075,
    "number": 17,
    "key": "92:17",
    "textAr": "وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا ٱلْأَتْقَى",
    "textEn": "But the righteous one will avoid it",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 596,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6076,
    "number": 18,
    "key": "92:18",
    "textAr": "ٱلَّذِى يُؤْتِى مَالَهُۥ يَتَزَكَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "[He] who gives [from] his wealth to purify himself",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 596,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6077,
    "number": 19,
    "key": "92:19",
    "textAr": "وَمَا لِأَحَدٍ عِندَهُۥ مِن نِّعْمَةٍ تُجْزَىٰٓ",
    "textEn": "And not [giving] for anyone who has [done him] a favor to be rewarded",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 596,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6078,
    "number": 20,
    "key": "92:20",
    "textAr": "إِلَّا ٱبْتِغَآءَ وَجْهِ رَبِّهِ ٱلْأَعْلَىٰ",
    "textEn": "But only seeking the face [i.e., acceptance] of his Lord, Most High.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 596,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6079,
    "number": 21,
    "key": "92:21",
    "textAr": "وَلَسَوْفَ يَرْضَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And he is going to be satisfied.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 596,
    "hizb": 60
  }
]